org.drip.state.inference

Class LatentStateSequenceBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.state.inference.LatentStateSequenceBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SegmentSequenceBuilder

    public class LatentStateSequenceBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements SegmentSequenceBuilder
    LatentStateSequenceBuilder holds the logic behind building the bootstrap segments contained in the given Stretch. It extends SegmentSequenceBuilder by implementing/customizing the calibration of the starting as well as the subsequent segments.
    Author:
    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
